Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.26,0:02:32.80,Main,Hotdog lady,0,0,0,,Oh! Hey, Kamina! \N Another day, another song?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.80,0:02:34.34,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Yeah! Cause...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.34,0:02:38.01,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,...when I turn fifteen, \N I’m gonna enter the Grand Prix!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.33,0:03:09.36,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Dance with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.13,0:03:26.93,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,Who’s your partner, miss?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.15,0:03:26.93,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,{\an8}U-Uhh...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.04,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,I’m scouting for one righ—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.90,0:03:36.90,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Hey! I {\i1}love{\i0} your singing voice!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.32,0:03:39.37,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,How’d you like to sing with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.81,0:03:45.09,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Just take a look!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.29,0:03:49.08,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Look at everyone’s smiles!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.77,0:03:52.84,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,They’re all waiting for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.72,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Hey, Tyltto!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.72,0:04:17.95,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,How about you become my partner?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.25,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Three years have passed!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.37,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,The day’s finally here!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.91,0:04:34.38,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,{\q2}It’s my fifteenth birthday! \N Now I can send in my application for the Grand Prix!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.38,0:04:41.78,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,{\q2}Renée and her partner made their debut at fifteen, \N so we can make our debut at fifteen too, can’t we?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.44,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,We’ll finally get to stand on the stage!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.44,0:04:54.54,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,All right, Tyl! \N The Grand Prix’s next month!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.54,0:04:56.21,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Let’s practice again today!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.13,0:05:00.91,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Then, how about we race \N to our usual park?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.84,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Ready... Bang!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.92,0:05:08.50,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,I went the wrong way again...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.50,0:05:12.83,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,That pose looks great, Tyl!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.75,0:05:14.96,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Step, step, step...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.96,0:05:16.09,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,We’re syncing up!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.09,0:05:19.26,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Our harmony sounds incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.26,0:05:22.68,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Gonna keep on practicing \N in your dreams?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.72,0:05:27.31,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,How about we touch up \N the pre-chorus dance routine a bit?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.93,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Let’s do our best out there today!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.81,0:05:35.47,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,What’s wrong, Tyl? You’re so tense!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.47,0:05:37.40,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Relax, relax!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.50,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Now, let’s go!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.33,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,Are you all excited?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.96,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,Time to watch the birth \N of a brand-new star!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.59,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,So then...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.34,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,Let the Twinkle Grand Prix...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.83,0:05:58.99,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,...begin!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.15,0:06:08.31,Main,Backstage man A,0,0,0,,How is she not here yet?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.71,0:06:11.03,Main,Backstage woman,0,0,0,,She’s not gonna make it in time.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.93,0:06:13.30,Main,Backstage man A,0,0,0,,What’s her contact info?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.94,0:06:16.19,Main,Backstage man B,0,0,0,,Let’s just put the next girl on first.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.58,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,It was crazy crowded \N and I got separated from Tyl!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.58,0:06:32.71,Main,Woman A,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Looks like the Grand Prix’s \N really heating up!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.46,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Tyl, where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.46,0:06:37.27,Main,Woman B,0,0,0,,That last performance was amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.27,0:06:39.08,Main,Woman C,0,0,0,,I wonder what the next girl will be like.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.59,Main,Woman B,0,0,0,,Oh, I can’t wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.97,0:06:54.56,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Tyl, your singing voice \N is just so lovely!{Somewhat echoes 03:33}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.56,0:06:56.65,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,How’d you like to sing with me?{03:37}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.99,0:07:03.32,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Our harmony sounds incredible!{05:17}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.22,0:07:06.32,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Tyl, you’re the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.20,0:07:08.99,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,I believe in you, Tyl!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.37,0:07:33.90,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Tyl!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.90,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,You evolved?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.45,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Your neck’s grown really long!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.10,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,So cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.95,0:07:45.74,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,It appears your Tyltalis \N has found the perfect partner.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.82,0:07:48.45,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.24,0:07:51.20,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.37,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,You’re starring in the Grand Prix, no?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.04,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.46,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.46,0:07:57.74,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.46,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,You were this close \N to missing your chance...{Caster: Thank you for waiting! Finally...}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.88,0:08:15.44,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,...to prove that \N what I saw was real...{lit. Your chance to prove that my eyes didn’t deceive me.}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.64,0:08:20.65,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,...and you would one day \N sing upon a grand stage.{In thinking that one day, you would sing on a big stage.}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.60,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,There are places...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.74,0:08:28.82,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,...that Pokémon alone, \N and people alone, cannot reach.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.43,0:08:33.45,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,But Pokémon and people both share \N the same desire to have their songs heard.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.92,0:08:35.08,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,Now, Tyltalis!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.77,0:08:40.08,Main,Renée,0,0,0,,Show me the unbeatable bond \N between you and your partner!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.52,Main,Man,0,0,0,,It Mega Evolved!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.76,Main,Woman,0,0,0,,I’ve never seen that before!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.76,0:10:13.04,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,Ahh... That was so much fun!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.97,0:10:17.04,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,You really turned into \N a whole new you, Tyl!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.72,0:10:22.73,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,I never would’ve guessed the necklace \N the lady with sunglasses gave us was a Key Stone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.73,0:10:25.92,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,It just stings a little \N that we didn’t win.{It’s just too bad we didn’t win.}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.78,0:10:32.03,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,What’re you doing? That tickles!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.03,0:10:43.05,Main,Kamina,0,0,0,,How about we make some big fireworks \N with Destroyer Beam next time?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
