Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.01,0:02:40.81,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}Ah, I just can't wait
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.81,0:02:42.77,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}For that twinkling stage
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.77,0:02:45.56,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}And at my side, that's right! My partner
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.56,0:02:49.44,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}Surrounded by the smiles of all my fans
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.44,0:02:54.07,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}I'll shine brighter on the stage than anyone
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.07,0:02:57.66,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}All the anxious people, all the people who've made mistakes,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.66,0:03:01.49,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}all the shy people, and all the people who're nervous
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.87,0:03:08.92,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}I'll take every last one of them and make them smile
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.92,0:03:11.71,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}I'm Kamina, Kamina
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.84,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}And when my day comes
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.84,0:03:17.39,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}Along with an unbeatable partner
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.39,0:03:21.89,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}That shining stage so far away, is where we will stand
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.89,0:03:24.85,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}I'm Kamina, Kamina
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.97,0:04:01.85,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}With your bravery, I can finally picture it
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.85,0:04:05.39,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}That marvelous scene, why it's right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.39,0:04:10.06,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}Surely together, we'll get to go even further
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.06,0:04:14.32,Song EN,,0,0,0,,{\q2\blur1\pos(960,95)}than we could alone
